<p>*Note: In all our Lindy Beginners courses all participants learn to lead and follow. We have seen, that this leads to the best learning results. (ELEF = everybody leads, everybody follows). You can read more about the benefits of double role learning here: <a href="https://bravenewswing.de/elef/">https://bravenewswing.de/elef/</a></p>
